name: Ewok Tribesman
Lore: 'Members of Chief Chirpa''s Ewok tribe are courageous in battle. They seek to impress older members of the tribe. Deploys only on Endor.',
Text: 'Power and forfeit +1 for each Light side icon at same Endor site. When forfeited at same site as your Ewok of ability > 1, may satisfy all remaining attrition against you.',
